---

<section class="bg-navy text-white py-20 md:py-28">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 text-center">
    <p class="animate-on-scroll text-orange font-bold text-sm tracking-widest mb-4" data-animation="fade-in">PRICING</p>
    <h2 class="animate-on-scroll text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-black mb-2" data-animation="fade-up">
      業界最安値への挑戦。
    </h2>
    <p class="animate-on-scroll text-lg sm:text-xl text-white/80 mb-10" data-animation="fade-up" data-delay="0.1s">
      「サブスク！経営コンサルティング」
    </p>

    <div class="animate-on-scroll" data-animation="scale-in" data-delay="0.2s">
      <div class="inline-block bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-3xl px-10 sm:px-16 py-10 sm:py-14 border border-white/20">
        <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mb-2">月額</p>
        <div class="flex items-end justify-center gap-1">
          <span class="font-accent font-extrabold text-6xl sm:text-7xl md:text-8xl text-orange">20,000</span>
          <div class="flex flex-col items-center pb-1 sm:pb-2">
            <span class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold leading-tight">円</span>
            <span class="text-sm text-white/60">（税別）</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-4 text-white/50 text-sm space-y-1">
          <p>※年間契約・次年度自動更新</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="animate-on-scroll mt-10 flex items-center justify-center gap-3 text-white/70" data-animation="fade-up" data-delay="0.4s">
      <svg class="w-10 h-10 text-orange/60" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M3 3h2l.4 2M7 13h10l4-8H5.4M7 13L5.4 5M7 13l-2.293 2.293c-.63.63-.184 1.707.707 1.707H17m0 0a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4zm-8 2a2 2 0 100 4 2 2 0 000-4z"></path></svg>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg">
        ディナー1回分の投資で、<br class="sm:hidden" />御社の経営企画室が手に入ります。
      </p>
    </div>

    <p class="animate-on-scroll mt-6 text-white/40 text-sm" data-animation="fade-in" data-delay="0.5s">
      対象：中小企業経営者、個人事業主向け
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
